{"tid":194493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯及伊朗警告美國若對敘利亞再有行動　將作出回應","createTime":"2017-04-10T04:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T04:25:57.000Z","uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"372b9a01c35391149a7b8a043f977d313e303f81","tid":194493,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T04:13:43.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯及伊朗警告美國，對敘利亞的行動已經超出底線，若果美國再向敘利亞再進行軍事行動，將會作出回應，加強支援敘利亞。有關聲明由俄羅斯、伊朗以及支持敘利亞總統巴沙爾的民兵一同發表。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統普京及伊朗總統魯哈尼通電話，指責美國違反國際法，攻擊敘利亞是不容否認的侵略，要求調查在敘利亞伊德利卜發生的化武事件，但要求客觀、不應有先入為主的態度。雙方重申，準備好加強雙邊合作打擊恐怖主義，維護中東和平。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1324286-20170410.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1324286-20170410.htm&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=76b8fad6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1324286-20170410.htm&h=28bb2b26\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1324286-20170410.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c93fb7199fdea70ab39b63e2a5303d0df430a968","tid":194493,"uid":33650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"trump真係驚都未驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e09b84fde9a907f5545c8ad4d266f4d13b58b7d","tid":194493,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T04:18:39.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯以前打左先講"},{"pid":"e97352de0714593806f523982f712d604604182a","tid":194493,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T04:25:57.000Z","msg":"真正痴線佬邊會警告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}